pr_title: Optimize Twitter dashboards updates and data
pr_body:
- Now the data is being handled in the [TwitterData](https://github.com/r-community/twitterdata) repository, which updates the data daily. The dashboard now reads directly from this data source.
- This Pull Request also sets up a way for the dashboard to be updated daily in the central repository through the use of a custom GitHub Action, which also runs daily right after the data update in TwitterData. This GitHub Action re-renders the dashboard and pushes the result to the central repository. The Action can also be triggered manually if desired.

I've tested the Action in a private repository of mine so it should work as intended.
